  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency documentation to v5.3.3",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation\">documentation</a> from <code>v5.3.2</code> to <code>v5.3.3</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>documentationjs/documentation</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"533\">5.3.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/55307ce13e962f168008c7313e90f06d02a4ed73\"><code>55307ce</code></a> chore(release): 5.3.3</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/e4781ebf548bcaff9541fe4248e60e6237ec938f\"><code>e4781eb</code></a> fix: Fix the split in HTML at 33/67% instead of calculating percentages (#&#8203;939)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/c43701b6723f868b6d14ce31c21f21db57ecbb77\"><code>c43701b</code></a> docs: Fix grammar in getting started</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/69ce427f0206a3b8541baca9b57146bee67fe8ff\"><code>69ce427</code></a> chore: Update yarn.lock</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/303b7929acc230197facd9d89a3521302001cf53\"><code>303b792</code></a> chore: Update mime within 1.x range to address regex vuln (#&#8203;934)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/7a548eb444123fe69743f43eb1f6545dd95d166e\"><code>7a548eb</code></a> fix(html): Display all levels of parameter properties. (#&#8203;933)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/e203df51c0653cf9ccb875cff820d13741ec22dd\"><code>e203df5</code></a> chore: Replace babel-preset-es2015 on babel-preset-env Fixed #&#8203;931 (#&#8203;932)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/8b8e6a2ba09e5e070adcaa274b607fdfb2e8babf\"><code>8b8e6a2</code></a> Added ignore mime package. Close #&#8203;926</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/227db1c9ee493b8fac033714e230ed1c3defe78b\"><code>227db1c</code></a> chore: updated yargs Fixed #&#8203;836</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/10bbba5402133dae0e46b28f2e7d1dca92480158\"><code>10bbba5</code></a> chore: Updated devDependencies</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/f375b2ba755999eb989ab54cc238b73dd1132a33\"><code>f375b2b</code></a> chore: updated flow js</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/337b7a639e33db9f3712d34a69e185c777521f46\"><code>337b7a6</code></a> chore: updated jest 21 version</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/334559ea1ed8a8bd56987a993758236f2b84ae8a\"><code>334559e</code></a> chore(package): update coveralls to version 3.0.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/2b74956b18d4556ed746e3f8f1281f794c475876\"><code>2b74956</code></a> fix(package): update github-slugger to version 1.2.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/c6bf13db381d2ba8b54783a65efdd3e86e429dbc\"><code>c6bf13d</code></a> test: Even more tests</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/e02b91f8d5df7c9ed130c2b9e559f88898969f3b\"><code>e02b91f</code></a> chore: Update tests for release</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
